# Copy to .env — never commit .env. No mainnet keys, ever (see CLAUDE.md).
#
# On-chain testing is the agreed direction. The signature-level negative checks
# (RS-NEG) need only a throwaway key (no funds). The settlement-level checks
# (RS-PAY group) additionally need a funded Base Sepolia payer.
#
# Base Sepolia (eip155:84532):
# X402_TESTNET_RPC_URL=https://sepolia.base.org
# X402_TESTNET_PAYER_KEY=   # testnet-only throwaway key, fund via Circle faucet
# X402_TESTNET_USDC=0x036CbD53842c5426634e7929541eC2318f3dCF7e
